OL,7,FAround 3,000 female workers from
OL,8,FBirmingham City Council could strike
OL,9,Fover equal pay claims.
OL,11,FMembers of GMB Union will be will
OL,12,Ftoday (July 1st ), begin a
OL,13,Fconsultative vote on strike action.
OL,15,FSome schools in the city are expected
OL,16,Fto take part in the initial ballot.
OL,18,FThe council admitted it had an equal
OL,19,Fpay liability in June 2023.
