OL,7,FIn December 2024, the council reached
OL,8,Fan agreement to settle thousands of
OL,9,Fequal pay claims that had pushed the
OL,10,Flocal authority to the brink of
OL,11,Fbankruptcy.
OL,13,FA formula had been agreed between the
OL,14,Fcouncil and unions - which valued the
OL,15,Fclaims at at least #250 million.
OL,17,FGMB Regional Organiser Rachel Fagan
OL,18,Fsaid: "It's been nearly two years
OL,19,Fsince the Council finally admitted
OL,20,Fthey had an equal pay crisis on their
OL,21,Fhands.
