OL,7,F"Since then, we've seen missed
OL,8,Fopportunity after missed opportunity
OL,9,Fto do right by women workers.
OL,11,F"Meanwhile, thousands of women are
OL,12,Fstill being short changed and paid
OL,13,Fless than they are worth.
OL,15,F"GMB members have been promised
OL,16,Fsettlement by the Autumn, but progress
OL,17,Fis too slow.
